Релиз инсталлера (bump patch, сборка, `/var/www/installer`, commit, push):

```bash
cd /home/debian/qwertystock && ./scripts/release-installer-and-push.sh
```

Только сборка и www без bump/git: `cd /home/debian/qwertystock && ./scripts/publish_installer_to_www.sh`

